channel.title: Mopar Problems?
channel.description:
Well, I've been trying to download private server clients for like the past hour, i cant figure out how to connect. Honestly.
What do i put next to Username, Password, and Server.
Do i use my Username from forums?
And please give me server IP's because i have non at the moment, and i want them :[
Sorry for causing trouble and asking stupid questions, but i wanna try this out :mad:

Type you username as you want it to be, unless the server requirs you to register.
Type no pass unless you have to register in which case visit the servers site and do
When you get ingame type ::pass passhere to change your pass to something you want.
The ip can be found in the servers section or what the one posted.
